<varlistentry id="options.NoPPosition">
	<term>NoPPosition</term>
	<listitem>
		<para>Species that afterstep should ignore the  PPosition  field  for
		the specified window, in other words, the window can't choose where
		to place  itself.   Adherence  to  the  PPosition  field  is
		required for some applications.</para>
	</listitem>
</varlistentry>
